properties.id: The ID of the API key.
properties.token: The token of the API key
properties.salt: Salt used to create the API key token.
properties.redacted: The redacted form of the api key's token. this is useful when showing portion of the token.
properties.title: The title of the API key
properties.type: The type of the API key. Can be `secret` or `publishable`.
properties.last_used_at: The date the API key was last used.
properties.created_by: The ID of the user that created the API key
properties.revoked_by: The ID of the user that revoked the API key
properties.revoked_at: The date the API key was revoked.
